PRP therapy. 
I going to be doing an offer on this....
RRP £175 per treatment
Advised in packages of three, one month apart.

£100 per treatment  for a limited time only! 

What is PRP? 
A PRP Facial, also known as a PRP facial or plasma facial combines platelet rich plasma (PRP) with Microneedling or the Vampire Facial. The PRP comes from the patient’s own blood, which is drawn and processed prior to the treatment by spinning the sample in a centrifuge to isolate the plasma. After the PRP serum is ready, the facial begins with a Microneedling treatment.
Then the serum can be injected into the areas of concern. 
The benefits include:

Reduced Scarring
Improved Skin Texture 
Improves fine lines and wrinkles
Repairs skin 

